{"tid":362441,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企有好多蟻同穀牛點搞好","createTime":"2017-08-17T02:27:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T08:34:51.000Z","uid":44747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a8acd60b32c802bc53643adde8343a718a71da47","tid":362441,"uid":44747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T02:27:09.000Z","msg":"近排天氣越來越熱就滋生唔少既昆蟲仔，本來個範圍由廚房慢慢伸延至客廳，甚至係房<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。依家成日形住形住佢地係我身上爬來爬去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都唔知啲蟻同穀牛點解吽到咁多出黎，雖然穀牛係米入面吽出黎，但明明有蓋冚實好...但都仲可以走得黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴打有咩方法可以一次過殺哂啲蟻同穀牛，又可以有方法去防治到佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d582a78760a4c86c7031383e8888e1bf02a6a44e","tid":362441,"uid":31990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T02:29:55.000Z","msg":"谷牛易搞，放上y拍"},{"pid":"19b3cade69fae33bfa22f1028374f99d56923bb5","tid":362441,"uid":52468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T08:34:51.000Z","msg":"水攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}